===Adverb===
{{en-adv|-}}

# to a [[great]] [[extent]] or [[degree]]; [[extremely]]; [[exceedingly]]
#: ''You’re '''very''' tall.''
# [[true]], [[truly]]
#: ''He tried his '''very''' best.''

====Usage notes====
* When used in their senses as degree adverbs, "very" and "[[too]]" never modify verbs.

